    "body": "## Problem\r\n\r\n`c_CTRL-{G,T}` stop cycling once an `'incsearch'` command includes an offset such as `/blah/e`.\r\n\r\n`do_search()` already parses the pattern and offset separately but `may_do_command_line_next_incsearch()` cycles on the raw cmdline text instead.\r\n\r\nPartially fixes #22228.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nRefactor pattern/offset parsing from `do_search()` to be used in the command-line incsearch path so `c_CTRL-{G,T}` keep selecting matches.\r\n\r\n***NOTE***: this does not fully resolve #22228 (see my comment).",
    "closed_at": null,
